[{"Id": 1016640, "EnglishTitle": "PLEASE NOTE: Be it clear that the reason for presenting Translation is to understand Salaat and to recite in Arabic with concentration because reciting Salaat other than Arabic language (or Transliteration) is not correct.", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Waazeh rahe keh tarjuma-e-namaz pesh karne ki asal wajah namaz samajh ke Arabi mein khuzoo aur tawajjoh ke saath namaz padhna hai. Kyu’n keh Arabi ya Roman-Arabi (Transliteration) ke siwa kisi aur zabaan mein namaz padhna sahih nahin hai.", "UrduTitle": "واضح رہے کہ ترجمۂ نماز پیش کرنے کی اصل غرض نماز سمجھ کے عربی میں خضوع اور توجہ کے ساتھ نماز پڑھنا ہے۔ کیوں کہ عربی کے سوا کسی اور زبان میں نماز پڑھنا صحیح نہیں ہے۔ اس لئے ہر ایک کے لئے نماز کی حد تک قرآن و عربی سیکھنا واجب ہے۔", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014971, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "This prayer has been reported by a big number of scholars, such as Shaikh Mufeed, Shaikh Tusi, Sayyid Ibn Tawus, and many others, from Imam Sadiq (a). However, according to the report of Sayyid Ibn Tawus, the way of offering this prayer is as follows: When you have an urgent need and you wish Almighty Allah to grant it for you, you may observe fasting on 3 successive days; Wednesday, Thursday and Friday. On Friday, you may bath (ghusl) yourself, dress yourself with a new, clean costume, go up to the highest point in your house, and offer a 2 unit prayer. Then, you may raise your hands towards the sky and say the following supplication…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shaikh Mufeed, Shaikh Toosi aur Syed ibne Tawoos jaise bohot se buzurg olma ne Hazrat Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) naql kiya hai. Chunaan-che Syed ibne Tawoos ki riwaayat ke mutaabiq is ki kaifiyat yu hai keh jab tumhe koi mushkil dar-pesh ho aur us mein Khuda ki madad matloob ho to musalsal 3 din yaani Wednesday, Thursday aur Friday ko roza rakho, Friday ke roz ghusl kar ke paak o paakeeza libaas pehno aur ghar ki sab se unchee chhat (roof) par ja kar 2 rakat namaz baja laawo aur phir haatho’n ko aasmaan ki taraf buland kar ke is tarah se kaho…", "UrduDescription": "شیخ مفید ؒ،شیخ طوسی ؒ اور سید ابن طاؤس ؒ جیسے بہت سے بزرگ علماء نے حضرت امام جعفر صادق ؑ سے نقل کیا ہے۔ چنانچہ سید ابن طاؤس ؒ کی روایت کے مطابق اس کی کیفیت یوں ہے جب تمہیں کوئی مشکل در پیش ہو اور اس میں خدا کی مدد مطلوب ہو تو مسلسل تین دن یعنی بدھ، جمعرات، جمعہ کے روزے رکھو، جمعہ کے روز غسل کرو پاک وپاکیزہ لباس پہنو اور گھر کی سب سے اونچی چھت پر جاکر ۲ رکعت نماز بجا لاؤ اور پھر ہاتھ آسمان کی طرف بلند کر کے کہو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014972, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, I have resided in Your court due to my full acquaintance with Your Oneness, Self-independence, and that there is none to settle my need save You. I have known, O my Lord, that whenever Your graces are poured down on me in hoards, my need to You becomes more urgent. I have been inflicted by the distress of…", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mai yaqeenan Teri baargah mein haazir hu keh Teri wah-daaniyyat aur Teri be-neyaazi ko jaanta hu aur yeh bhi keh Tere alaawa koi meri haajat poori nahi kar sakta aur ay Parwardigaar mai jaanta hu keh jo jo Teri ne’mate’n badhti hai Teri taraf meri ehtiyaaj badhti jaati hai, ab mujhe yeh aur yeh mushkil aan padhi hai…", "Urdu": "اے معبود! میں یقیناً تیری بارگاہ میں حاضر ہوں کہ تیری وحدانیت اور تیری بے نیازی کو جانتا ہوں اور یہ بھی کہ تیرے علاوہ کوئی میری حاجت پوری ہی نہیں کر سکتا اور اے پروردگار میں جانتا ہوں کہ جوں جوں تیری نعمتیں بڑھتی ہیں تیری طرف میری احتیاج بڑھتی جاتی ہے اب مجھے یہ اور یہ مشکل آن پڑی ہے۔۔۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE HALAL-TO BE-SAA-HATE-KA LE-MA’RE-FATEE BE-WAHDAA-NIYYATE-KA WA SAMA-DAN NIYYATE-KA WA ANNA-HU LAA QAADE-RAN A’LAA QAZAAA-E HAAJA-TEE GHAIRO-KA WA QAD A’LIM-TO YAA RABBE ANNA-HU KULLA-MAA TAZAA-HARAT NE’MATO-KA A’LAIY-YASH TADDAT FAAQA-TEE ILAIY-KA WA QAD TARA-QANEE HAMMO KAZA WA KAZA…", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّىْ حَلَلْتُ بِسَاحَتِكَ لِمَعْرِفَتِىْ بِوَحْدَانِيَّتِكَ وَصَمَدًا نِيَّتِكَ وَاَنَّهٗ لَا قَادِرًا عَلٰى قَضَاۗءِ حَاجَتِىْ غَيْرُكَ وَقَدْ عَلِمْتُ يَا رَبِّ اَنَّهٗ كُلَّمَا تَظَاهَرَتْ نِعْمَتُكَ عَلَىَّ اشْتَدَّتْ فَاقَتِىْ اِلَيْكَ وَقَدْ طَرَقَنِىْ هَمُّ كَذَا وَكَذَا۔۔۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014973, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "You should now mention your problem and then keep on, saying…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ab apni haajaat bayaan karo aur phir kaho…", "UrduDescription": "کَذَاوکَذَا کی جگہ اپنی حاجات بیان کرکے کہو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014974, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "...About relieving me from this distress, You have full knowledge and You need no direction and You are Limitless and You do not have to think about it. I therefore beseech You in the name of Your Name that You put on the mountains; so, they were carried away from the roots, You put on the heavens; so, they were rent asunder, on the stars; so, they were spread, and on the earth; so, it was made a vast expanse. I also beseech You in the name of the Right that You deposited with Muhammad, may Allah bless him and his Household, and with Ali, Hasan, Husain, Ali, Muhammad, Ja`far, Moosa, Ali, Muhammad, Ali, Hasan, and the Argument, peace be upon them, (I beseech You) to send blessings upon Muhammad and his Household, settle my need for me, make easy what is difficult in it, and save me from the intricate part of it. If you do, then all praise be to You. If you do it not, then all praise be to You, because You are neither biased in Your judgment, nor accused in Your decree, nor prejudicing in Your justice.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "…aur Tu usey poora karna jaanta hai, bata ne ki zaroorat nahi, Tu wus’at rakhta hai Tujhe zehmat nahi, pas sawaal karta hu Tere naam ke waaste se keh jise Tu pahaado’n par rakhe to reza reza ho jaaye, aasmaano par rakhe to paash paash ho jaaye, sitaaro’n par rakhe to girne lag jaaye, zameen par rakhe to chatyal ho jaaye, sawaal karta hu us haq ke waaste se jise Tu ne qaraar diya hai Hazrat Muhammad Mustafa (s.a.w.a) aur Hazrat Ali (a.s), Hazrat Hasan (a.s), Hazrat Husain (a.s), Hazrat Ali (a.s), Hazrat Muhammad (a.s), Hazrat Jafar (a.s), Hazrat Moosa (a.s), Hazrat Ali (a.s), Hazrat Muhammad (a.s), Hazrat Ali (a.s), Hazrat Hasan (a.s) aur Hazrat Hujjat (a.t.f.s) ke saath yeh keh rehmat naazil farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unke Ahlebait (a.s) par aur yeh keh meri haajat poori kar, jo mushkil hai aasaan farma aur sakhtiyo’n mein madad kar. Pas agar Tu aisa kare to Tere liye hamd hai aur na kare to bhi Tere liye hamd hai keh Tere faisle mein zulm ka guzar nahi, Teri qaza mein ghalti nahi aur Tere adl mein khaami nahi hai.", "Urdu": "۔۔۔اور تو اسے پورا کرنا جانتا ہے بتانے کی ضرورت نہیں تو وسعت رکھتا ہے تجھے زحمت نہیں پس سوا ل کرتا ہوں تیرے نام کے واسطے سے کہ جسے تو پہاڑوں پر رکھے تو ریزہ ریزہ ہوجائیں آسمانوں پر رکھے تو پاش پاش ہو جائیں ستاروں پر رکھے توگرنے لگ جائیں زمین پر رکھے تو چٹیل ہو جائے سوال کرتا ہوں اس حق کے واسطے سے جسے تو نے قرار دیا ہے حضرت محمد مصطفیٰ ؐاور حضرت علی ؑ، حضرت حسنؑ، حضرت حسینؑ، حضرت علیؑ،حضرت محمد ؑ،حضرت جعفر ؑ، حضرت موسیٰ ؑ، حضرت علی ؑ، حضرت محمد ؑ، حضرت علی ؑ،حضرت حسن ؑ اور حضرت حجت ؑ کے ساتھ یہ کہ تو رحمت فرما محمدؐ اور ان کے اہل بیت ؑ پر اور یہ کہ میری حاجت پوری کر جو مشکل ہے آسان فرما اور سختیوں میں مدد کر پس اگر تو ایسا کرےتو تیرے لئے حمد ہے اور نہ کرے تو بھی تیرے لئے حمد ہے کہ تیرے فیصلے میں ظلم کا گزر نہیں تیری قضا میں غلطی نہیں اور تیرے عدل میں خامی نہیں ہے۔", "RArabic": "…WA ANTA BE-KASH-FEHI A’ALE-MUN GHAIRO MO-A’LLA-MIN WAASE-U’N GHAIRO MOTA-KALLE-FIN FA-AS-ALOKA BISME-KAL LAZEE WA WAZA’TAHU A’LAL JEBAA-LE FA-NOSE-FAT WA WAZA’TAHU A’LAS SAMAA-WAATE FAN-SHAQQAT WA A’LAN NOJOO-ME FAN-TASA-RAT WA A’LAL ARZE FO SOTE-HAT WA AS-ALOKA BIL HAQQIL LAZEE JA-A’LTA-HU I’NDA MOHAMMADIN SALLAL LAAHO A’LAIY-HE WA AALE-HI WA I’NDA A’LIYYIN, WAL HASANE, WAL HUSAINE, WA A’LIYYIN, WA MOHAMMADIN, WA JA’FARIN, WA MOOSA, WA A’LIYYIN, WA MOHAMMADIN, WA A’LIYYIN, WAL HASANE, WAL HUJJATE A’LAIHE MUS-SALAAMO, ANTO SALLEYA A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AHLE-BAIYTE-HI WA AN TAQZE-YA LEE HAAJA-TEE WA TO-YASSIR-LEE ASEE-RAHAA WA TAKFE-YANEE MOHIMMA-HAA FA-IN FA-A’LTA FA-LAKAL HAMDO WA IN LAM TAF-A’L FA-LAKAL HAMDO GHAIRO JAAA-E-RIN FEE HUKME-KA WA LAA MUTTA-HEMIN FEE QAZAAA-E-KA WA LAA HAAA-E-FIN FEE A’DLE-KA.", "ArabicText1": "۔۔۔وَاَنْتَ بِكَشْفِهٖ عَالِمٌ غَيْرُ مُعَلَّمٍ وَاسِعٌ غَيْرُ مُتَكَلِّفٍ فَاَسْئَلُكَ بِاسْمِكَ الَّذِىْ وَضَعْتَهٗ عَلَى الْجِبَالِ فَنُسِفَتْ وَ وَضَعْتَهٗ عَلَى السَّمٰوَاتِ فَانْشَقَّتْ وَعَلَى النُّجُوْمِ فَانْتَثَرَتْ وَعَلَى الْاَرْضِ فَسُطِحَتْ وَاَسْئَلُكَ بِالْحَقِّ الَّذِىْ جَعَلْتَهٗ عِنْدَ مُحَمَّدٍ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَآلِهٖ وَعِنْدَ عَلِىٍّ وَالْحَسَنِ وَالْحُسَيْنِ وَعَلِىٍّ وَمُحَمَّدٍ وَجَعْفَرٍ وَمُوْسٰى وَعَلِىٍّ وَمُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلِىٍّ وَالْحَسَنِ وَالْحُجَّةِ عَلَيْهِمُ السَّلَامُ اَنْ تُصَلِّىَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاَهْلِ بَيْتِهٖ وَاَنْ تَقْضِىَ لِىْ حَاجَتِىْ وَتُيَسِّرَلِىْ عَسِيْرَهَا وَتَكْفِيَنِىْ مُهِمَّهَا فَاِنْ فَعَلْتَ فَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ وَاِنْ لَمْ تَفْعَلْ فَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ غَيْرُ جَآئِرٍ فِىْ حُكْمِكَ وَلَا مُتَّهَمٍ فِىْ قَضَاۗئِكَ وَلَاحَاۗئِفٍ فِىْ عَدْلِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, 